### Test gRPC Follow/Unfollow Endpoints
### Prvo se ulogujte da dobijete token

### 1. Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/gateway/stakeholders/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "vukasin",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Test Follow User (koristiti ID iz prethodnog odgovora)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/gateway/followers/1/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Test Unfollow User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/gateway/followers/1/unfollow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Test Follow Same User Again (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/gateway/followers/1/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Test Follow Self (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/gateway/followers/3/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
